The paper deals with the task of product classification using textual descriptions, which falls under the domain of natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves the use of machine learning algorithms for prediction, which falls under the domains of information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and computer vision (cs.CV).
